By Lisa Shock on Sunday, May 13, 2001 - 10:45 am:

For the most part, the hard to find monsters are ones where there are limited entries in the CD list. If a monster has more than 30 CDs listed in the CD list, do not post it.

However, I think there are certain breeds that people would like to raise more than other breeds. Once we get all the pure-breeds posted, many mixed breeds will be pointless.

Also, some monsters may be hard to find on CD, but fairly easy to make through combos. Ones that have all types hard to find is much more desirable, like Zilla & Undine -which is why I posted them right away.

Don't duplicate any breeds, we have to save space around here, somehow.
